    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you develop a sixth sense that helps you avoid traps. You gain a +2 bonus on <em>Perception</em> checks made to notice traps. You also gain a +1 bonus on <em>Reflex</em> saves to avoid traps and a +1 <em>dodge bonus</em> to AC against attacks made by traps. These bonuses increase by +1 at 7th level and for every four <em>sorcerer</em> levels you gain thereafter (to a maximum of +5 at 19th level). This bonus stacks with that provided by a <em>rogueâ€™s</em> <em>trap sense</em> and similar abilities.</p>"
